<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head><meta charset="utf-8"><title>Listing Rejected</title></head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
  <h1 style="color: #dc2626;">Business Listing Rejected</h1>
  <p>Hi {{recipientName}},</p>
  <p>We regret to inform you that your business listing <strong>{{businessName}}</strong> has been rejected.</p>
  {{#if reason}}
  <p><strong>Reason:</strong> {{reason}}</p>
  {{/if}}
  <p>Please review the feedback and update your listing before resubmitting for approval.</p>
  <p>If you believe this was a mistake, please contact our support team.</p>
  <p>Best regards,<br>The Digital Directory Team</p>
</body>
</html>
